home_txt_1: No More Waste collects food donations from retailers and individuals. Anyone in need can apply for a portion of these donations. As an association, we rely on volunteers to help with the collection and dispatch of foodstuffs on our rounds.
home_txt_car: Access our car exchange service by paying a small fee.
home_txt_cooking: Take part in cooking classes and advice sessions to avoid food waste.
home_txt_donation: Contribute to our cause by making a donation to support our efforts.
home_txt_project: Get help from the community for small DIY jobs.
home_txt_volunteer: Join our team of volunteers and help us collect and distribute food.
